 as Gaussian RBF,\nespecially in the case of high dimensional problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2014 16:11:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Feb 2015 18:49:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-24"}
