e\ndecline in star-formation rate of the universe is happening.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2014 20:00:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2016 17:25:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-15"}
