rther derive envelope function equations that allow the\nmethod to be used empirically, in which case certain parameters in the envelope\nfunction equations will be fitted to experimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2014 14:22:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-29"}
