der range of speed distributions, this leads to larger\nuncertainties in the particle physics parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2014 10:57:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 May 2015 08:58:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
